    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is offset by the strength of the literature-review evidence demonstrating that quasi-static ASTM F1717 conditions are representative of the COU loading regime. The overall credibility profile is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level determination for regulatory submission.",
